text: Joshua Keck Harder (born August 1, 1986) is an American politician and businessman who in 2023 became the U.S. representative for California's 9th congressional district, after he became the 10th district from 2019 to 2023. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:United States representatives from California Category:People from Stanislaus County, California
